                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The firehoof minotaur snorts and stomps fire as they hunt their prey, inspiring terror. The minotaur makes an Intimidation check to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Demoralize] all living creatures within @Template[emanation|distance:60]{60 feet} who can hear the minotaur but not clearly see them (whether the minotaur is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Hidden], or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Undetected]). Roll once and apply the result to all creatures. If the targets have their vision effected by smoke or a similar effect, the minotaur gains a +4 circumstance bonus to this check. Each target is temporarily immune for 10 minutes.</p>"
